---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us — Società Filarmonica di Turriaco" lang="en" currentPage="chisiamo">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <p class="intro-quote">
        <em>The only band in the province of Gorizia to have carried out its activities uninterruptedly across three centuries, it is one of the most historically rich ensembles in the entire Friuli Venezia Giulia region.</em>
      </p>

      <p>The first &ldquo;banda di Turriaco&rdquo; was founded in 1870, on the initiative of a small group of local music enthusiasts.</p>

      <p>Its first steps were taken under the direction of maestro Guglielmo Szubert, and it was formally constituted as the &ldquo;Società Filarmonica di Turriaco&rdquo; in December 1900. After various vicissitudes — including an internal split that led, at the turn of the century, to the coexistence of two distinct bands — it found its definitive form in 1920, maintaining it until March 2017 when, by unanimous decision of the members' assembly, it was transformed into a Social Promotion Association (APS).</p>

      <p>A witness to the historical evolution that transformed the Isonzo lands from Habsburg territory to an integral part of the Italian state, the ensemble represents an exceptional <em>trait d'union</em> between the most recent musical trends and the rhythms and sounds of Central European culture.</p>

      <p>The ensemble currently consists of around thirty active members, joined — depending on the occasion — by friends who enjoy making music together with us.</p>

      <p>Independent in its organisational and administrative management, the Association is governed by a board of directors elected by the members' assembly.</p>

      <figure style="margin: 40px 0; text-align: center;">
        <img
          src={`${base}/asset/images/fotobanda.jpg`}
          alt="Group photo — Società Filarmonica di Turriaco"
          style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 4px;"
        />
        <figcaption style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-text-light, #888); font-style: italic; margin-top: 8px;">The Turriaco Band at the 2025 Christmas Concert</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

